只會傷害自己，中國應把精神集中在國內。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報導，至於何時會對價值2000億美元中國商品加徵25％關稅，白宮首席經濟顧問庫德洛（Larry Kudlow）7日表示，還要再等待官員完成公眾意見的評估。<br />\n面對川普政府的蓄勢待發。中國官媒《人民日報》11日刊出評論指出，從2010年開始中國就遇到外部的挑戰與麻煩，都與美國有關，對此，不要心存僥倖，也別驚慌失措，最重要的是從容應對，更專注做好自己的事情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180912/1256769.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180912%2F1256769.htm&d=0ae027bs3124tcF0V6cgnP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b1aae9e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180912/1256769.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:39:32.000Z","msg":"成鳩人將人地搞鳩佢嘅事提升到國家統一嘅層次, 就好似我叫個麻甩佬執番個煙頭, 佢問我係咪想搞散佢頭家一樣咁白痴."},{"pid":"a5437b823f0daf0a1559ec291d82812455c414c3","tid":815351,"uid":143078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"變成7個大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1901fa62a61e72915f9d439c01c66f999f98381c","tid":815351,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a702d5930710dfa587e16b5bffc52c03c07a06","tid":815351,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7fc38afec96cb7ce6b873b0db49f79e8ce5881d","tid":815351,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e4bfcbc5dd1e3ce2744914cbc4b3d2cc45db6a3","tid":815351,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"on9 , 講到話浸浸想蝗分七份真係over哂。 咁講等同話美國會用一切武力去搞到蝗蟈分裂無分別。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:35:30.000Z","msg":"美國分解左蘇聯, 要用武力嗎?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"咩年代仲講打講殺武裝起義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n緊係打殘你經濟最快趣啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"凍結所有支共狗官海外資產，都夠嚇死佢地。"},{"pid":"5fd62e3e79d1e8b8a38a2b4bbfb7b9404f27a0be","tid":815351,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f433850335c7880df5c9ae90eb13f13